Title: Cast
Kitchen Sink: Vanessa Hudgens, Ed Westwick, Mackenzie Davis

Title: Synopsis
Kitchen Sink:
Vampires, humans and zombies used to get 
	along in Dillford, but then something unexpected 
	arrived and now it's humans vs. vampires vs. zombies
	 in all-out mortal combat. It's up to three 
	teenagers to try to get things back to normal.
